vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to CanTex Pittsburg, LLC for the use of a total of approximately 980 square feet of aerial space to install, occupy, maintain and utilize three canopies without premise signs over portions of Levee and Pittsburg Streets rights-of­way located near the intersection of Levee and Pittsburg Streets - Revenue: General Fund $300.00 one-time fee, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
